tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Played Wells Fargo Championship after open qualifying and missed the cut...Made three starts on the Web.com Tour...Finished T123 at the final stage of Web.com Tour Q-School.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Won 2009 Pinehurst Intercollegiate Championsip...Finished as co-medalist at the 2010 NCAA East Regional...Was named an Honorable Mention All-American in 2010.
tourBios.personal: Enjoys fly fishing and hunting...Lists playing in 2015 Wells Fargo Championship as the biggest thrill of his professional career...Favorite pro teams are Pittsburgh Penguins and Carolina Panthers...Favorite TV shows are "Big Bang Theory" and "House of Cards." ...Twitter handle is @tj03howe...Personal motto is "Success takes you where character sustains you."
